    "summary": "This paper demonstrates interferometric single-shot fermion-parity readout in InAs–Al hybrid nanowire devices using a gate-defined triple quantum dot coupled to a proximitized nanowire. The key result is a flux-dependent bimodal quantum-capacitance signal with h/2e periodicity, enabling parity assignment in a single shot with ~1% assignment error and millisecond-scale dwell times, while also constraining trivial Andreev-state explanations.",
